Class ExecutionStep

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cpirvu.ExecutionStep
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrintableExecution
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImageExecutionStep, ImageFileExecutionStep

    abstract class ExecutionStep
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrintableExecution
    An ExecutionStep is the smallest unit of processing power that can be ran at a specific time.
